    This license does not grant trademark rights. Unauthorized use of trademarks will mean that you are liable for trademark infringement.

4. Severability

    If any provision of this license is held to be invalid, illegal, or unenforceable under any applicable law or regulation, such invalidity, illegality, or unenforceability does not effect the validity, legality, or enforceability of the remaining provisions of this license.
    In the event that any provision of this license is held to be invalid, illegal, or unenforceable, both you and the author agree to replace such provision with a valid, legal, and enforceable provision that most closely approximates the intent and effect of the original provision.
    The remaining provisions of this license shall continue to be in full force and effect, and the parties shall continue to be bound by the terms and conditions of this license as if the invalid, illegal, or unenforceable provision had not been included.

